00:47:25.885 --> 00:47:27.011
Her name is Katy.

00:47:28.304 --> 00:47:29.972
What is your Chinese name?

00:47:33.977 --> 00:47:35.269
Ruiwen.

00:47:36.312 --> 00:47:38.480
Names are sacred, Ruiwen.

00:47:38.648 --> 00:47:40.649
They connect us
not only to ourselves,

00:47:40.734 --> 00:47:42.526
but to everyone
who came before.

00:47:43.987 --> 00:47:45.654
<i><c.color80ffff>A funny story.</c>

00:47:45.822 --> 00:47:48.282
Some years ago,
a terrorist from America

00:47:48.366 --> 00:47:49.783
needed a boogeyman

00:47:49.951 --> 00:47:52.578
to bring your country
to its knees.

00:47:52.746 --> 00:47:55.414
So, he appropriated
The Ten Rings.

00:47:55.498 --> 00:47:56.498
My Ten Rings.

00:47:56.583 --> 00:47:59.084
But because
he didn't know my actual name,

00:47:59.169 --> 00:48:00.544
he invented a new one.

00:48:01.171 --> 00:48:03.130
<i><c.color80ffff>Do you know the name he chose?</c>

00:48:04.966 --> 00:48:06.508
The Mandarin.

00:48:06.676 --> 00:48:09.636
He gave his figurehead
the name of a chicken dish.

00:48:10.055 --> 00:48:11.472
<i><c.color80ffff>And it worked.</c>

00:48:11.639 --> 00:48:13.432
America was terrified.

00:48:14.309 --> 00:48:15.893
Of an orange.

00:48:17.687 --> 00:48:18.979
<i><c.color80ffff>The truth is,</c>

00:48:19.147 --> 00:48:22.024
I've had many names
throughout my life.

00:48:22.734 --> 00:48:25.152
The Warrior King, Master Khan,

00:48:25.236 --> 00:48:27.362
the most dangerous man
on Earth.

00:48:27.697 --> 00:48:31.742
For years, I thought that was
all I was meant to be.

00:48:34.579 --> 00:48:37.456
But when I met their mother,

00:48:38.208 --> 00:48:40.000
everything changed.

00:48:54.224 --> 00:48:57.851
<i><c.color80ffff>She showed me a part of myself
I didn't know was there.</i></c>

00:49:00.605 --> 00:49:03.482
<i><c.color80ffff>It was like I was seeing
the world for the first time.</i></c>

00:49:13.660 --> 00:49:17.204
<i><c.color80ffff>She gave up everything
so we could be together.</i></c>

00:49:20.458 --> 00:49:22.126
<i><c.color80ffff>And so did I.</i></c>

00:49:37.183 --> 00:49:38.851
You know who's in there?

00:49:39.018 --> 00:49:40.853
Say, "Hello, little sister!"

00:49:47.318 --> 00:49:48.777
<i><c.color80ffff>After all those years,</i></c>

00:49:48.862 --> 00:49:50.445
<i><c.color80ffff>I finally found something</i></c>

00:49:50.613 --> 00:49:52.781
<i><c.color80ffff>worth growing old for.</i></c>

00:49:58.246 --> 00:50:00.622
My real name is Wenwu.

00:50:01.457 --> 00:50:04.042
<i><c.color80ffff>She was the only one
who called me that.</c>

00:50:05.712 --> 00:50:07.504
And when she died...

00:50:10.717 --> 00:50:13.051
<i><c.color80ffff>I was lost for many years.</c>

00:50:15.763 --> 00:50:17.764
<i><c.color80ffff>But I'm not lost any more.</c>

00:50:22.145 --> 00:50:23.604
<i><c.color80ffff>When you children ran away,</c>

00:50:23.771 --> 00:50:26.315
<i><c.color80ffff>I was so desperate
to connect with your mother,</c>

00:50:26.482 --> 00:50:29.693
<i><c.color80ffff>I threw myself back into
the studies of her village.</c>

00:50:30.278 --> 00:50:32.070
<i><c.color80ffff>The legendary Ta Lo.</c>

00:50:33.281 --> 00:50:34.448
<i><c.color80ffff>I wasn't able</c>

00:50:34.532 --> 00:50:36.783
<i><c.color80ffff>to find the secret path
to the village entrance,</c>

00:50:36.951 --> 00:50:40.495
but I did find
what they are hiding.

00:50:41.039 --> 00:50:43.582
<i><c.color80ffff>There's a gate
deep in their mountains.</c>

00:50:44.250 --> 00:50:46.919
<i><c.color80ffff>Your mother
is waiting for us there.</c>

00:50:49.881 --> 00:50:51.506
I know this is a lot.

00:50:51.716 --> 00:50:55.552
I might not have believed it
if she didn't tell me herself.

00:50:56.387 --> 00:50:58.013
What are you talking about?

00:50:58.514 --> 00:51:00.599
I was sitting right here
in this seat,

00:51:01.017 --> 00:51:03.060
deep in my research...

00:51:04.270 --> 00:51:06.146
and she spoke to me.

00:51:06.940 --> 00:51:09.691
<i><c.color80ffff>It was like
she was standing in this room.</c>

00:51:09.859 --> 00:51:12.694
I could feel her breath
on my cheek

00:51:12.779 --> 00:51:14.738
and her hand on my back.

00:51:16.282 --> 00:51:18.533
<i><c.color80ffff>She told me she needs my help.</c>

00:51:20.286 --> 00:51:21.495
To do what?

00:51:22.288 --> 00:51:24.665
To save her from her people.

00:51:27.835 --> 00:51:29.670
After we fell in love,

00:51:29.754 --> 00:51:32.464
your mother wanted us
to live in Ta Lo.

00:51:32.632 --> 00:51:34.633
She asked permission
from the elders,

00:51:34.717 --> 00:51:35.884
and they refused.

00:51:36.052 --> 00:51:38.262
They said I wasn't worthy.

00:51:40.056 --> 00:51:41.390
She would still be with us.

00:51:41.474 --> 00:51:44.101
We would all be
living there together.

00:51:44.894 --> 00:51:46.603
