00:53:17.528 --> 00:53:19.446
<i><c.color80ffff>on qlngming Jie.</c>

00:53:20.406 --> 00:53:22.949
<i><c.color80ffff>To get through,
you need to know the route</c>

00:53:23.034 --> 00:53:25.410
<i><c.color80ffff>and the exact time it opens.</c>

00:53:29.832 --> 00:53:31.458
