01:03:37.564 --> 01:03:39.023
Morris is very clear.

01:03:39.608 --> 01:03:41.484
The way through
is all about timing.

01:03:41.986 --> 01:03:43.695
Okay, but how long
are we talking?

01:03:43.862 --> 01:03:45.571
<i><c.color80ffff>Like, hours? Days?</c>

01:03:45.739 --> 01:03:48.366
Friends,
I am but a transitory vessel

01:03:48.450 --> 01:03:49.867
for the infinite wisdom
of a creature

01:03:50.035 --> 01:03:52.286
far more advanced than
we'll ever truly understand.

01:03:52.913 --> 01:03:54.539
What he sees, what he feels

01:03:54.623 --> 01:03:56.332
of this vast, unknown universe

01:03:56.500 --> 01:03:58.418
is beyond anything
our simple brains can...

01:03:58.502 --> 01:03:59.919
Oh. You can go.

01:04:00.337 --> 01:04:01.379
What?

01:04:01.463 --> 01:04:03.256
Go. You can go. He says "go. "

01:04:26.488 --> 01:04:27.947
You should speed up.

01:04:28.615 --> 01:04:29.615
What? Why?

01:04:31.827 --> 01:04:32.994
Katy, go, go, go!

01:04:36.999 --> 01:04:38.082
Morris says,

01:04:38.167 --> 01:04:40.043
- "Hard right on three. "
- What?

01:04:40.210 --> 01:04:41.210
Two...

01:04:41.295 --> 01:04:42.295
Hard right where?

01:04:42.379 --> 01:04:43.755
Now.

01:04:51.013 --> 01:04:52.305
And left.

01:04:56.727 --> 01:04:58.311
It's all about staying
in the pocket.

01:04:58.479 --> 01:05:00.146
- What pocket?
- We're in it now.

01:05:00.314 --> 01:05:01.981
What happens if
we don't stay in the pocket?

01:05:02.149 --> 01:05:03.149
The forest eats us.

01:05:03.317 --> 01:05:04.776
Eats us? What does that mean?

01:05:04.943 --> 01:05:06.486
He says it eats us.
Go left.

01:05:14.703 --> 01:05:16.746
- Watch your back!
- Stay in the pocket.

01:05:16.914 --> 01:05:18.498
- How close is it?
- Five metres.

01:05:18.665 --> 01:05:20.416
- Stay in the pocket.
- What is that in feet?

01:05:20.584 --> 01:05:21.584
Really fricking close.

01:05:21.752 --> 01:05:22.752
Stay in the pocket.

01:05:22.920 --> 01:05:24.462
Will you just stop saying,
"Stay in the pocket"?

01:05:31.053 --> 01:05:33.179
One last right,
then straight on to the end.

01:05:41.230 --> 01:05:42.563
You might wanna hurry up.

01:05:42.731 --> 01:05:44.565
What do you think I'm doing?

01:05:46.193 --> 01:05:47.235
We're not gonna make it.

01:05:50.405 --> 01:05:51.989
I'm coming home, Mummy.

01:06:04.294 --> 01:06:07.255
Morris says,
"Great job, everyone. "

01:06:08.674 --> 01:06:11.551
Now, all we have to do
is go through that waterfall,

01:06:11.718 --> 01:06:13.511
and we're pretty much there.

01:07:03.854 --> 01:07:04.896
<i><c.color80ffff>Bloody hell.</c>

01:07:05.063 --> 01:07:06.814
<i><c.color80ffff>I think those birds
are on fire.</c>

01:07:06.899 --> 01:07:09.275
Really? Oh.

01:07:09.568 --> 01:07:11.777
Morris says it's normal.

01:07:11.945 --> 01:07:14.280
They're old mates of his.

01:07:48.190 --> 01:07:50.191
That's a weird horse.

01:07:51.610 --> 01:07:53.361
<i><c.color80ffff>What's it looking at me for?</c>

01:08:56.883 --> 01:08:59.010
Hi there!

01:08:59.261 --> 01:09:01.178
I am Xu Shang-Chi.

01:09:01.805 --> 01:09:04.598
<i><c.color80ffff>This is my sister, Xu Xialing.</c>

01:09:04.766 --> 01:09:07.310
<i><c.color80ffff>We're Ying Li's children.</c>

01:09:11.189 --> 01:09:12.690
This is my friend, Katy.

01:09:12.858 --> 01:09:16.485
Get in your car and go home!

01:09:16.653 --> 01:09:19.155
Please. You don't understand.

01:09:25.579 --> 01:09:26.996
<i><c.color80ffff>Guang Bo!</c>

01:09:28.373 --> 01:09:30.541
What are you doing?

01:09:31.168 --> 01:09:33.336
<i><c.color80ffff>Put down your weapons!</c>

01:09:36.298 --> 01:09:37.965
Shang-Chi.

01:09:38.425 --> 01:09:39.550
Xialing.

01:09:39.718 --> 01:09:42.970
I'm your aunty Nan.

01:09:44.723 --> 01:09:47.433
I've waited so long to meet you.

01:09:57.110 --> 01:09:58.736
You look like your mother.

01:10:06.578 --> 01:10:07.703
Hi, I'm Katy.

01:10:07.913 --> 01:10:09.288
Welcome to Ta Lo, Katy.

01:10:09.373 --> 01:10:10.956
Oh, thank you.

01:10:16.755 --> 01:10:19.256
<i><c.color80ffff>Look who has found
his way home!</c>

01:10:19.925 --> 01:10:21.175
I'm not a threat.

01:10:21.343 --> 01:10:23.469
Just an entertainer.

01:10:23.637 --> 01:10:25.221
Morris can vouch for me.

01:10:27.182 --> 01:10:28.557
We don't have much time.

01:10:29.017 --> 01:10:30.351
Our father is coming.

01:10:38.443 --> 01:10:41.404
Our people have been
here for over 4,000 years,

01:10:41.571 --> 01:10:44.365
preparing for something
we hope will never happen.

01:10:44.533 --> 01:10:47.076
<i><c.color80ffff>We are the keepers
of the Dark Gate,</c>

01:10:47.244 --> 01:10:49.620
sworn to protect this realm
and yours

01:10:49.704 --> 01:10:52.289
from the evil
that's locked behind it.

01:10:53.125 --> 01:10:55.334
Our dad is coming
here to open that gate.

01:10:55.877 --> 01:10:57.878
He thinks
you're holding our mom there.

01:10:59.172 --> 01:11:00.673
Why would he think that?

01:11:00.841 --> 01:11:02.049
<i><c.color80ffff>She told him.</c>

01:11:02.217 --> 01:11:04.260
He says he can hear her
asking for help.

01:11:06.680 --> 01:11:08.681
Is he wearing the rings?

01:11:08.849 --> 01:11:10.975
<i><c.color80ffff>He hasn't taken them off
since she died.</c>

01:11:12.894 --> 01:11:14.520
What do they have to do
with all this?

01:11:18.442 --> 01:11:20.526
The realm of Ta Lo
stretches far beyond

01:11:20.610 --> 01:11:22.486
the shores
of our small village.

01:11:22.654 --> 01:11:26.323
We have cities that surpass
any in your universe,

01:11:26.491 --> 01:11:29.201
<i><c.color80ffff>rich with culture and history.</c>

01:11:29.369 --> 01:11:31.370
<i><c.color80ffff>Thousands of years ago,</c>

01:11:31.538 --> 01:11:34.790
<i><c.color80ffff>all of our people
lived in peace and prosperity,</c>

01:11:35.876 --> 01:11:39.003
<i><c.color80ffff>until the attack
of the Dweller-in-Darkness.</c>

01:11:39.629 --> 01:11:41.046
<i><c.color80ffff>He came with his army,</c>

01:11:41.131 --> 01:11:44.175
<i><c.color80ffff>devouring every soul
in their path,</c>

01:11:44.342 --> 01:11:48.012
<i><c.color80ffff>and with each kill,
they grew stronger.</c>

01:11:48.680 --> 01:11:51.223
After decimating
our largest cities,

01:11:51.391 --> 01:11:54.810
they were headed to
your universe to do the same.

01:11:54.978 --> 01:11:58.355
<i><c.color80ffff>The leaders of Ta Lo sent
their strongest warriors here</c>

01:11:58.523 --> 01:12:01.734
<i><c.color80ffff>to stop them from reaching
the portal to your world.</c>

01:12:02.319 --> 01:12:05.446
<i><c.color80ffff>But our ancestors
were no match for them.</c>

01:12:06.573 --> 01:12:09.575
Until The Great Protector

01:12:09.701 --> 01:12:13.245
<i><c.color80ffff>joined their fight
and turned the tide.</c>

01:12:13.955 --> 01:12:16.957
<i><c.color80ffff>Together, they pushed
the Dweller and his army</c>

01:12:17.042 --> 01:12:18.250
<i><c.color80ffff>into the Dark Gate</c>

01:12:18.418 --> 01:12:20.878
<i><c.color80ffff>and locked it behind them.</c>

01:12:22.839 --> 01:12:26.258
Our people have guarded
that gate ever since,

01:12:26.426 --> 01:12:29.887
empowered by the magic
of The Great Protector

01:12:30.055 --> 01:12:32.348
and the gift that she gave us.

01:12:43.985 --> 01:12:44.985
Dragon scales.

01:12:45.153 --> 01:12:46.820
Makes very good armour.

01:12:48.949 --> 01:12:50.991
Your father isn't the first
to come here

01:12:51.076 --> 01:12:52.326
to open the Dark Gate.

01:12:52.911 --> 01:12:55.162
<i><c.color80ffff>Many have tried and failed
over the centuries,</c>

01:12:55.330 --> 01:12:57.665
<i><c.color80ffff>and they all had one thing
in common.</c>

01:12:57.832 --> 01:12:58.832
They were lured here

01:12:58.917 --> 01:13:01.043
by the voice of something
on the other side.

01:13:01.836 --> 01:13:04.713
<i><c.color80ffff>A voice that promised them
their greatest desires.</c>

01:13:07.175 --> 01:13:11.345
So you think soul eaters
are talking to our dad?

01:13:12.138 --> 01:13:15.474
They know The Ten Rings have
the power to break them free.

01:13:19.813 --> 01:13:20.813
Oh.

01:13:23.441 --> 01:13:25.025
Here you go.

01:13:25.277 --> 01:13:26.277
Oh.

01:13:26.820 --> 01:13:28.279
To the range.

01:13:29.447 --> 01:13:31.490
What? Okay.

01:13:32.242 --> 01:13:34.910
Looks like I'm gonna go
deliver some dragon arrows.

01:13:35.120 --> 01:13:36.537
Oh, you're gonna deliver
some dragon arrows?

01:13:36.621 --> 01:13:37.913
Yeah.
Make myself useful, you know.

01:13:38.081 --> 01:13:39.081
Thank you.

01:13:41.126 --> 01:13:42.835
Let's go see your mother.

01:13:57.517 --> 01:14:00.102
I just love how you guys know
exactly what you wanna do,

01:14:00.312 --> 01:14:03.105
and you spend your whole life
getting really good at it.

01:14:03.273 --> 01:14:04.857
I wish I was more like that.

01:14:05.025 --> 01:14:07.109
It's like every time I get
moderately good at something,

01:14:07.277 --> 01:14:09.528
I just quit
and start something new.

01:14:09.696 --> 01:14:11.614
But I just know my own limits,

01:14:11.781 --> 01:14:14.408
and I'm not gonna waste
my time chasing something

01:14:14.492 --> 01:14:16.327
that will ultimately be
a disappointment for me.

01:14:16.411 --> 01:14:17.453
That's not me.

01:14:17.537 --> 01:14:18.996
Guang Bo.

01:14:20.248 --> 01:14:21.582
Let her shoot.

01:14:24.961 --> 01:14:28.631
If you aim at nothing,
you hit nothing.

01:14:52.113 --> 01:14:53.739
<i><c.color80ffff>You were everything to her.</c>

01:14:55.408 --> 01:14:57.868
She knew that one day
you would find your way here

01:14:58.036 --> 01:15:00.788
and asked me to prepare
something for your arrival.

01:15:23.353 --> 01:15:25.270
After losing someone like her,

01:15:25.355 --> 01:15:27.981
it's easy to feel alone
in this world.

01:15:28.650 --> 01:15:30.317
But you're not.

01:15:30.485 --> 01:15:32.736
You are children
of this family,

01:15:33.321 --> 01:15:35.656
and I welcome you home.

01:16:03.309 --> 01:16:05.144
You're not
in your father's house any more.

01:16:06.896 --> 01:16:11.024
In Ta Lo, we train as equals.

01:16:12.777 --> 01:16:16.655
You've been in the shadows
long enough, my child.

01:16:36.050 --> 01:16:37.259
Guang Bo, you saw that?

01:16:38.011 --> 01:16:39.344
<i><c.color80ffff>That was tight!</c>

01:16:52.734 --> 01:16:54.651
My mother was the only one
who could beat him.

01:16:56.237 --> 01:16:58.030
Show me how she did it.

01:17:05.288 --> 01:17:06.789
No, sorry.

01:17:06.956 --> 01:17:08.540
Sorry. Offside, offside.

01:18:09.269 --> 01:18:11.478
Your mother knew
who she was.

01:18:12.230 --> 01:18:13.397
Do you?

01:19:19.422 --> 01:19:22.466
You are a product
of all who came before you.

01:19:23.426 --> 01:19:27.262
The legacy of your family,
the good and the bad,

01:19:28.056 --> 01:19:30.390
it is all a part
of who you are.

01:19:34.771 --> 01:19:36.855
Stop hiding, nephew.

01:19:37.690 --> 01:19:39.733
It only prolongs the pain.

01:20:12.183 --> 01:20:14.726
<i><c.color80ffff>We'll be together soon.</c>

01:20:21.150 --> 01:20:22.150
Sir.

01:20:24.821 --> 01:20:26.321
The men are ready.

01:20:27.365 --> 01:20:29.157
The passage will open at dawn.

01:20:30.118 --> 01:20:31.743
I'll prepare the vehicles.

01:20:55.893 --> 01:20:57.853
<i><c.color80ffff>Lead with your breath.</c>

01:20:58.312 --> 01:21:01.273
<i><c.color80ffff>Look into your heart,</c>

01:21:01.441 --> 01:21:04.776
<i><c.color80ffff>the light and the dark.</c>

01:21:04.944 --> 01:21:09.031
<i><c.color80ffff>To know yourself,</c>

01:21:09.198 --> 01:21:13.118
<i><c.color80ffff>you must face them both.</c>

01:21:28.217 --> 01:21:30.135
<i><c.color80ffff>Your husband tried to destroy us.</c>

01:21:30.720 --> 01:21:33.388
The Iron Gang is here
to repay that debt.

01:21:34.015 --> 01:21:35.932
My husband is not the man
he used to be.

01:21:36.726 --> 01:21:38.101
<i><c.color80ffff>It doesn't matter.</c>

01:21:39.353 --> 01:21:42.606
Your business with him has nothing
to do with my children.

01:21:45.526 --> 01:21:47.402
They can go,

01:21:47.570 --> 01:21:51.364
but someone has to pay.

01:21:56.037 --> 01:21:57.871
Xialing. Shang-Chi.

01:21:58.039 --> 01:21:59.039
Go inside.

01:21:59.165 --> 01:22:01.958
I'm going to talk to our guests.

01:22:07.965 --> 01:22:10.801
But you don't have your powers.

01:22:13.513 --> 01:22:15.555
Shang-Chi, you have nothing to fear.

01:23:37.805 --> 01:23:39.014
<i><c.color80ffff>Mama.</c>

01:23:41.642 --> 01:23:42.809
<i><c.color80ffff>Mama.</c>

01:24:01.329 --> 01:24:02.537
Papa.

01:24:11.839 --> 01:24:14.883
She told me I could change.

01:24:16.385 --> 01:24:19.638
That I could leave my past behind.

01:24:22.058 --> 01:24:24.559
But she was wrong.

01:24:27.772 --> 01:24:30.398
If I hadn't taken them off,

01:24:31.317 --> 01:24:35.278
those men wouldn't have
dared to do this.

01:24:37.740 --> 01:24:40.492
And now they will pay for it.

01:25:34.922 --> 01:25:35.964
Where's your boss?

01:25:36.424 --> 01:25:37.424
I don't know!

01:25:37.842 --> 01:25:39.426
I swear I don't!

01:25:41.012 --> 01:25:42.595
Okay.

01:25:55.943 --> 01:26:00.697
A blood debt has to be
paid by blood.

01:26:01.532 --> 01:26:03.325
Will you help me?

01:26:33.272 --> 01:26:34.481
We found the man

01:26:34.565 --> 01:26:36.649
responsible for killing
your mother.

01:26:37.860 --> 01:26:40.945
It is your right
to finish this for both of us.

01:26:42.073 --> 01:26:43.698
And when you return,

01:26:43.866 --> 01:26:47.369
we will rebuild The Ten Rings
to what it once was.

01:27:08.891 --> 01:27:10.517
Been looking
everywhere for ya.

01:27:18.442 --> 01:27:19.651
You okay?

01:27:24.031 --> 01:27:27.409
I'm not who you think I am.

01:27:27.576 --> 01:27:29.411
You already apologised
for that. We're good...

01:27:29.578 --> 01:27:31.538
That's not what
I'm talking about.

01:27:33.833 --> 01:27:35.041
Okay.

01:27:36.627 --> 01:27:38.420
What... What is it?

01:27:44.009 --> 01:27:48.847
When my dad sent me to find
the man who killed my mom...

01:27:51.559 --> 01:27:53.768
I told you
I couldn't go through with it.

01:27:58.816 --> 01:28:00.316
I lied.

01:28:04.572 --> 01:28:06.865
I thought that
I could change my name,

01:28:07.032 --> 01:28:09.951
start a new life, pretend like
it never happened.

01:28:10.119 --> 01:28:11.327
But...

01:28:18.252 --> 01:28:20.503
She would hate
the person I've become.

01:28:27.219 --> 01:28:29.429
Your dad trained you
to be an assassin

01:28:29.513 --> 01:28:31.431
when you were seven.

01:28:32.183 --> 01:28:35.768
<i><c.color80ffff>He sent you on a hit at 14.</c>

01:28:37.730 --> 01:28:40.106
<i><c.color80ffff>You realise how messed up
that is, right?</c>

01:28:43.736 --> 01:28:46.237
My mom is dead because of him.

01:28:49.200 --> 01:28:51.951
And now he's coming
to destroy her home.

01:29:01.337 --> 01:29:04.589
A blood debt
has to be paid by blood.

01:29:07.510 --> 01:29:09.260
What are you saying?

01:29:12.806 --> 01:29:15.016
I'm gonna do
what he trained me to do.

01:29:21.023 --> 01:29:22.565
I'm gonna kill him.

01:30:10.030 --> 01:30:11.030
He's here.

01:30:23.377 --> 01:30:24.377
No!

01:30:24.461 --> 01:30:25.712
You're not ready.

01:30:25.879 --> 01:30:27.922
She stays here.

01:31:21.644 --> 01:31:23.227
Are you here
to help the people

01:31:23.312 --> 01:31:25.772
holding your own mother
captive?

01:31:26.190 --> 01:31:27.774
<i><c.color80ffff>She isn't back there.</c>

01:31:28.150 --> 01:31:29.150
You're being lied to

01:31:29.234 --> 01:31:31.402
by a creature
who wants to destroy us all.

01:31:32.863 --> 01:31:34.947
Is that what they told you?

01:31:35.532 --> 01:31:38.159
<i><c.color80ffff>I know my wife's voice.</c>

01:31:38.369 --> 01:31:40.912
I miss my sister
as much as you do,

01:31:41.080 --> 01:31:43.665
but this is not the way
to honour her memory.

01:31:43.832 --> 01:31:45.625
Did you honour her
when you turned her away

01:31:45.709 --> 01:31:46.709
from your gate?

01:31:46.835 --> 01:31:49.337
You fool. We turned you away.

01:31:49.505 --> 01:31:52.048
The sins of your past would have
destroyed this place.

01:31:52.383 --> 01:31:56.678
Be careful how you speak to me,
young man.

01:31:57.096 --> 01:32:00.890
I've lived ten of your lifetimes.

01:32:02.434 --> 01:32:04.060
Let me pass.

01:32:04.395 --> 01:32:06.437
We cannot do that.

01:32:25.416 --> 01:32:26.582
Burn it down.

01:33:30.522 --> 01:33:31.647
Stop him!

01:34:07.267 --> 01:34:10.269
Are you planning to stop me
all by yourself?

01:34:14.608 --> 01:34:16.025
I'm not afraid of you.

01:34:23.325 --> 01:34:24.534
Yes, you are.

01:34:30.165 --> 01:34:33.584
You've spent
your entire life afraid.

01:34:33.752 --> 01:34:35.795
Always running,

01:34:35.963 --> 01:34:37.255
always hiding.

01:34:52.479 --> 01:34:54.647
You were there
when they came for her,

01:34:54.815 --> 01:34:56.983
and you did nothing.

01:34:57.568 --> 01:35:00.444
You stood at a window
and watched her die!

01:35:35.272 --> 01:35:36.981
She was gone
and we needed you.

01:35:38.191 --> 01:35:41.402
But you chose those damn rings
over us.

01:35:45.490 --> 01:35:46.991
You trained your son
to be a killer.

01:35:48.201 --> 01:35:49.327
Is this what you wanted?

01:36:06.720 --> 01:36:08.387
Even if you could
bring her back,

01:36:10.182 --> 01:36:12.808
what makes you think she'd
want anything to do with you?

01:36:38.418 --> 01:36:40.127
<i><c.color80ffff>Save me.</c>

01:36:41.129 --> 01:36:43.464
<i><c.color80ffff>Save me, my dear.</c>

01:37:03.276 --> 01:37:05.152
<i><c.color80ffff>Save me.</c>

01:37:05.612 --> 01:37:08.030
I'm coming, my love.

01:37:49.614 --> 01:37:50.823
He breached the gate!

01:37:55.287 --> 01:37:56.495
Those things
are gonna kill us all

01:37:56.580 --> 01:37:58.164
if we don't work together.

01:37:58.331 --> 01:38:00.374
You think
I'm going to fall for that?

